. It was a celebration many people enjoyed... Why 8? One from each class... Cleric, Wizard, Enchanter, Magician, Necromancer, Shadowknight, Rogue, and Warrior. The child had be 12 or 13... It was Innoruuk's favorite age of the dark elf... when the person changed in many ways that would shock the man. A meeting was taken place at a Inn in the 3rd gate area. Each guildmaster was there with record of every 12 or 13 year old's information. Also the queen's advisor who was in charge of the event was there jotting it down... He stood up, &quot;Alright. We will go with the Casters first.. Clerics first, do all 4 caster groups then the rogue and warrior.&quot; He looked towards the old aged Guildmaster... He had lightblue robes draiped over him and he was holding a bible type of book of Innoruuk... He stood up slowly then stared at his list. &quot;Well.. I have 7 people born on this date, 4 who are 12-13. 3 females and 1 male.&quot; The advisor took a deep thought... &quot;Kill the male.&quot; The priest was confused, &quot;Wouldn't you want to kill a female?.. It would kill the outnumberance.&quot; The advisor shook his head, &quot;We will whipe out what is not needed... Who is the fool?&quot; The priest stared at his list... &quot;Heress... only a 3rd circle cleric. Alright.&quot; The advisor jotted it down quickly, &quot;Thank you...&quot; The old cleric then left the Inn because he did not want to talk about scheduled deaths... The wizards, enchanters, and magicians already had their's planned out.. &quot;Ok... a girl wizard named Alic, boy enchanter named Nexomius, and a boy mage named Sirius...&quot; The advisor mumbled to himself as he wrote it down. He then turned to the Necromancer/Shadowknight guildmaster... &quot;Alright Xon, who are the 2?&quot; The evil man stood up and grinned evily... &quot;The unlucky necromancer is a woman named Puzuzu, and the fool of a shadowknight is Jakkin.&quot; The advisor nodded... &quot;Great way to get rid of that troublemaker, aye?&quot; Xon laughed out loud and nodded in agreement... The rogue guildmaster then stood up swiftly.. &quot;I have decided to give our most skilled roguess to the guild.. Yuim.&quot; The advisor was confused, &quot;Why your most skilled?&quot; The rogue bowed then replied, &quot;Because Innoruuk deserves the best. Make this young man's torment to be remembered... If you know what I mean.&quot; The advisor shook his head saddly but wrote it down, &quot;Then be it.&quot; The warrior stood up and gave a gruff face... almost like a dwarf, &quot;We have chosen our weakest warriors.. Dian and Devius... The twins.&quot; The advisor nodded in recognition but questioned, &quot;Why the weakest when Innoruuk was offered the best by a ROGUE?&quot; The warrior stood up to his tallest, &quot;I do not worship this man... but we shall get rid of the filth and make the dark elven race perfect.&quot; He sat down and smiled in proud to himself.. the others snickered.  Xon stood up.. &quot;I wish to give my own ideas of torment if I could...&quot; The advisor then replied, &quot;Choose one, the other one is for crowd entertainment.&quot; Xon's eyes went red... &quot;I choose Puzuzu.&quot; They both laughed evily then after some more commotion.. Everyone departed.<br><br>Later on that day Puzuzu went to the guild just like a normal person goes to school... Xon was going to have all the members in a meeting. The young necromancer wondered who the 2 victims were for this 1000 years.. She ran to the meeting and sat by her friends AJ and Hellix... Some necromancers had already heard the word and stared at Puzuzu with big eyes. Puzuzu was confused, should she have had fixed her hair? She looked further down her row of seats and noticed many people were jabbering to a shadowknight who was cursing at them.. &quot;Leave me alone you bastards! I deserve no attention... Lord Xon does!&quot;.. AJ chuckled, &quot;Kiss ass...&quot; Puzuzu ignored her... she knew something eiry was going on. Suddenly black smoke filled the stage up ahead and Xon appeared.. Many of the older necromancers and shadowknights scowled in praise and howled in cheers... Puzuzu hated the noise.. it always sent a chill down her spine. <br><br>Xon's eyes were red... it seemed he was enjoying himself. Like usuall... He then used his loud, powerful voice to let everyone hear him... &quot;Hello my evil spawn... Necromancers..&quot; All the necromancers screeched... &quot; and Shadowknights..&quot; The shadowknights roared in echo... &quot;Welcome to the meeting tonight.. Have you all noticed that it's the 4000th year of the dark elven race!?!? We have gone far.... Well.. Cut to the chase.&quot; Many screamed.. &quot;I have chosen the victims.... these 2 shall be remembered for maybe the next 1000 years or so...&quot; Many people laughed... &quot;Congratulations Puzuzu and Jakkin.&quot; <br><br>Puzuzu was paralyzed.... she stared over at Jakkin who fell out of his chair.. Many people were pointing at him and saying.. &quot;YOU ARE THE ONE!&quot; None seemed to notice Puzuzu though... she didn't care. She was one of the flunking Necromancers.. almost everyone was amazed at Jakkin's talent. Why would Xon kill Jakkin out of all people?... Puzuzu understood why they would kill her, she was a big troublemaker. She liked the reputation but never knew this would happen... Xon always told her, &quot;Your day will come when you shall regret it you fool...&quot;<br><br>AJ and Hellix stared in awe at Puzuzu.. &quot;I can't believe it!&quot; Hellix started to screech, she seemed excited... &quot;I am THEE ONE's best friend!!&quot; Her and AJ started to dance... &quot;SHUT UP.&quot; Puzuzu yelled... &quot;How would you like to be the one who is being killed?...&quot; AJ shrugged.. &quot;I never will be that lucky.&quot; Suddenly Xon casted a trance spell that guided their eyes towards him.. &quot;Alright. This is how it goes.. Jakkin shall be have his torment put the way the crowd decides.. As for Puzuzu... It's time your demented guildleader showed you some of his stuff!&quot; He lifted his hands in praise and most of the guild cheered.. AJ and Hellix cheered... Puzuzu was mad stiff. &quot;Damn you.&quot; She said. She got up out of her chair and left the meeting room... How would she get out of this one? <p><center><br><img src="http://a0.cpimg.com/image/8A/CA/8481930-eaf4-014B01B8-.jpg"><br><font color=purple><br><b><br></b></font><a href="http://www.mines.edu/students/a/averheyd/">\m/Verbreiten Sie die Krankheit\m/</a><br>Fürchten Sie die Schwärzung...,  Hageln Satan</center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/umelmell.showPublicProfile?language=EN>melmell</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.theorderofthedragon.com/docs/fanart/cross.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>A_Idiot_666</span><br>  Posts: 204<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(2/7/02 8:30:01 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=152.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://a0.cpimg.com/image/8A/36/8501130-86a6-00800074-.jpg height=145 width=128></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> .</span><hr size=1> Puzuzu didn't understand it.. Why must they show honor in such a horrid way? Or was it just her?... She hated being a necromancer... Maybe she could show them. She walked down the street with her head hanging low. A couple richy people bumped into her then bowed, &quot;You are Puzuzu the Chosen are you not? Quite a honor... I would do anything to be in your place.&quot; That gave Puzuzu an idea.. &quot;Give me all you own and sure as heck I will...&quot; The man laughed and shook his head, &quot;Innoruuk has chosen, I will not deserve the natural flow of chance and choice..  I still wish it though.&quot; Puzuzu was dissapointed... These people seemed to take things so seriously. Life wasn't suppose to be that simple... Yes. You can change things... The 'flow of chance and choice' sucked anyways. :P<br><br>Puzuzu rolled her eyes at the excited chatter from the 2 dark elves as she walked further away from them. She had to hide. Hide forever maybe... She loved a wild reputation, being noticed, and famous but this was the type of famous she didn't ask for... She didn't want to sacrafice herself to abunch of suckers. Especially with the 'dreaded whore', her guildmaster, would choose her fate. &quot;Ick.&quot; she said to herself... Almost home. She wondered what her parents would do, they were alot like her. Hating all these 'brainwashed fools' and Innoruuk but still devoted themselves to him... They would probally bitch and moan with her but not do anything about it. <p><center><br><img src="http://a0.cpimg.com/image/8A/CA/8481930-eaf4-014B01B8-.jpg"><br><font color=purple><br><b><br></b></font><a href="http://www.mines.edu/students/a/averheyd/">\m/aegrotatio egrotatio\m/</a><br><font color=grey><font size=10><TABLE STYLE="filter:glow(color=#a2a2a2, strength=5)"><TR><TD><center>Timeo Cariosus Acerbus Abyssus</TABLE></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uspirits101.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Spirits101</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(2/9/02 7:25:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=152.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: .Good story</span><hr size=1> Very good story. Well thought out. So now i'm 